        Clause 159 [<span class="italic">Power to make provision corresponding to EC Regulation 2201/2003</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04265'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_876' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="bold">Baroness Crawley</span> moved Amendments Nos. 65A and 65B:
        <q>Page 77, line 26, after "Wales" insert "or Northern Ireland</q>
        <q>Page 77, line 33, after "Wales" insert "or Northern Ireland</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04266'>
