      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0661P0-04268'>
        <a name='S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_879'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-christine-crawley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_879' title='Link to this speech by Ms Christine Crawley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-christine-crawley" title="Ms Christine Crawley">Baroness Crawley</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Perhaps this would be an appropriate moment for the Committee to adjourn until Tuesday 25 May at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0661P0-04269'>
        <a name='S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_880'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-margaret-of-mar' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_880' title='Link to this speech by Ms Margaret of Mar' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-margaret-of-mar" title="Ms Margaret of Mar">The Deputy Chairman of Committees (The Countess of Mar)</a></cite>
